Studentereksamen (1959). Licentiatgrad i medicin (1966); dr.med. (1977). Afdelingslæge (Oulus Universitets Centralsygehus). Docent (Oulus Universitet). <> Næstformand for Det Nationale Samlingsparti (1991-1993). <> Rigsdagsmedlem (indtil 1995). Formand for Uddannelsesudvalget (1991-1995). <> Doktorafhandling: "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Adskillige videnskabelige udgivelser inden for medicin. <> Ridder af 1. klasse af Finlands Hvide Roses Orden.

Hochschulreife (1959). Lizentiatin der Medizin (1966); Doktor der Medizin (1977). Stationsoberärztin (Zentralkrankenhaus der Universität Oulu). Dozentin (Universität Oulu). <> Stellvertretende Vorsitzende der KOK (1991-1993). <> Mitglied des Finnischen Parlaments (bis 1995). Vorsitzende des Bildungsausschusses (1991- 1995). <> Dissertation "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Zahlreiche wissenschaftliche Veröffentlichungen auf dem Gebiet der Medizin. <> Ritterorden Erster Klasse der Finnischen Weißen Rose.

Ακαδημαϊκό Απολυτήριο (1959). Πτυχιούχος Ιατρικής (1966)· Διδάκτωρ Ιατρικής (1977). Διευθυντής Κλινικής (OYKS). Αναπληρώτρια Καθηγήτρια (Πανεπιστήμιο του 'Οουλου). <> Αντιπρόεδρος του Εθνικού Κόμματος Συνασπισμού της Δεξιάς (1991-1993). <> Βουλευτής (μέχρι το 1995). Πρόεδρος της Επιτροπής Πολιτισμού (1991-1995). <> Διδακτορική Διατριβή "Τhe effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Συγγραφεύς διαφόρων ιατρικών δημοσιευμάτων. <> Παράσημο Ιππότου Α' Τάξεως του Λευκού Ρόδου.

School leaving certificate (1959). Degree in medicine (1966). PhD in medicine (1977). Senior physician (University of Oulu Central Hospital). Lecturer (Oulu University). <> Deputy chairman, KOK party (1991-1993). <> Member of Parliament (until 1995). Chairman, Committee for Education and Culture (1991-1995). <> Doctoral thesis 'The effect of epidural analgesia for pain relief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism' (1977). Author of several medical publications. <> Order of the White Rose, First Class.

Bachiller Superior (1959). Licenciada en Medicina (1966); Doctora en Medicina y Cirugía (1977). Médico jefe de departamento (Hospital Central Universitario de Oulu). Profesora universitaria (Universidad de Oulu). <> Vicepresidenta de la KOK (1991-1993). <> Miembro del Parlamento de Finlandia (hasta 1995). Presidenta de la Comisión de Educación y Cultura (1991-1995). <> Tesis doctoral "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Numerosas publicaciones científicas en el campo de la medicina. <> Condecoración de Caballero de primera clase de la Orden de la Rosa Blanca de Finlandia.

Ylioppilastutkinto (1959). Lääketieteen lisensiaatti (1966); LKT (1977). Osaston ylilääkäri (OYKS). Dosentti (Oulun yliopisto). <> Kansallisen Kokoomuksen varapuheenjohtaja (1991-1993). <> Kansanedustaja (vuoteen 1995). Sivistysvaliokunnan puheenjohtaja (1991-1995). <> Väitöskirja "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Useita tieteellisiä julkaisuja lääketieteen alalta. <> Valkoisen Ruusun I luokan ritarimerkki.

Baccalauréat (1959). Docteur en médecine (1966). Doctorat d'État en médecine (1977). Médecin-chef de service (CHU d'Oulu). Chargé de cours (Université d'Oulu). <> Vice-président du KOK (1991-1993). <> Député au parlement finlandais (jusqu'en 1995). Président de la commission de la culture (1991-1995). <> Thèse de doctorat: ""The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Nombreuses publications scientifiques dans le domaine médical. <> Chevalier de la Rose Blanche de Première classe.

Maturità (1959). Laurea in medicina (dal 1966). Dottorato di Stato (1977). Medico primario (Policlinico universitario di Oulu). Professoressa all'Università di Oulu. <> Vicesegretario del Partito della Coalizione nazionale (1991-1993). <> Deputato nazionale (fino al 1995). Presidente della commissione per l'istruzione e la cultura (1991-1995). <> Tesi di dottorato: "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Numerose pubblicazioni scientifiche di medicina. <> Decorazione di prima classe della Rosa bianca.

Toelatingsexamen universiteit (1959). Licentiaat medicijnen (1966); Doctoraat medicijnen (1977). Chef-arts (Academisch Ziekenhuis Oulu). Docent (Universeit Oulu). <> Vice-voorzitter KOK (1991-1993). <> Lid Fins parlement (tot aan 1995). Voorzitter Commissie cultuur (1991-1995). <> Dissertatie "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Verscheidene medische publikaties. <> Ridder eerste klasse in de orde van de Witte Roos.

Ensino secundário (1959). Mestrado em Medicina (1966). Doutoramento em Medicina (1977). Chefe de serviço médico (OYKS). Professora do ensino superior (Univ. de Oulu). <> Vice-presidente do KOK (1991- 1993). <> Deputada ao Parlamento finlandês (até 1995). Presidente da Comissão da Cultura (1991-1995). <> Tese de doutoramento "The effect of epidural analgesia for painrelief during labour on maternal and fetal metabolism" (1977). Numerosas publicações científicas na área da medicina. <> Insígnia deprimeira classe da Ordem Finlandesa da Rosa Branca.
